This directory is the landing pad for real Skoda Roomster fault recordings
collected per docs/REAL_FAULT_COLLECTION.md. Empty in this commit; the
.gitkeep marker is here so the directory survives a fresh clone.

When a recording lands, it follows the naming convention documented in
data/real_faults/README.md:

  skoda_<faulttype>_<YYYYMMDD>_<runN>.csv
  skoda_<faulttype>_<YYYYMMDD>_<runN>.json   (sibling metadata)

CSVs in this directory are gitignored — they get checked in only after
review (file size, PII check on metadata).
